params.amount: Amount of DGNRS tokens to burn

constructor.details: Wires the predeployed DGNRS token and fixed addresses from ContractAddresses. DEPLOYMENT ORDER: 1. Deploy BondToken (DGNRS) with ContractAddresses.BONDS set to the precomputed bonds address 2. Deploy DegenerusBonds RNG is sourced from the game; bonds no longer request VRF directly.

params.beneficiary: Address to credit with bond score (uses msg.sender if zero address)

returns.scoreAwarded: Amount of score awarded based on deposit and player multiplier

params.amount: Amount of ETH (in wei) to credit as score
params.beneficiary: Address to credit with bond score

returns.scoreAwarded: Amount of score awarded based on amount and player multiplier

returns._0: Address of the shared DGNRS bond token

gameOverWithEntropy(uint256).details: Access: game only. Used by advanceGame to centralize RNG.

mintJackpotDgnrs(address,uint256,uint24).details: Game-only. Respects auto-burn preference; if enabled, registers burns directly.

params.beneficiary: Address to receive DGNRS tokens (or have burns registered if auto-burn enabled)
params.currLevel: Current game level (used for routing burns to correct maturity)

notifyGameOver().details: Sets gameOverStarted flag and records timestamp for expiry calculations.

returns._0: True if bond purchases are currently enabled, false otherwise

requiredCoverNext(uint256).details: Used by the game to check if sufficient liquidity exists for bond operations.

params.stopAt: Maximum required cover to calculate; returns stopAt+1 if exceeded (0 = no limit)

returns.required: Total ETH required to cover all bond obligations

runPresaleDailyFromGame(uint256,uint48).details: Access: game only. Pays buyer lane BURNIE, burn-lane BURNIE, and DGNRS lane.

params.enabled: True to enable auto-burn, false to disable

shutdownPresale().details: Manual flag; does not end presale until the next daily run.

sweepExpiredPools().details: Callable by anyone; destination is fixed to the vault.

constructor.notice: Initialize the bond system with precomputed dependencies.
